				<div class="resTitle section">


























<h2>
	
    Integrated Digital Option
    
	
</h2>


</div>

				

				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-opaque" id="f0727805-d672-461a-aabc-81e93e6896d4" >

    <p>The&nbsp;Integrated Digital (ID) Option&nbsp;is available to film and photography majors starting in third year. The Option is comprised of studio and lecture courses in image-based media and visual studies. The Option is designed to expand creative and analytical skills beyond the borders of film and photography. Areas such as multi-channel, titling, web-based image book design are among the many cross-platform, interactive art practices offered within the Integrated Digital Option.</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#f0727805-d672-461a-aabc-81e93e6896d4");});</script></div>

				

				
